---
title: Creamy Chicken Sausage & Tortelloni Soup  Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: Ever find yourself wondering, “Why have an average-sized bite of cheesy stuffed pasta, when you could have that same bite… but slightly bigger?” You’re asking the right questions, friend. That’s why our chefs created this dinner featuring tortelloni (the jumbo brother of tortellini), mixed with pan-seared chicken sausage and fresh spinach in a creamy, savory bowl of broth. Finish your bowls with Parmesan and scallions, and serve with a side of toasty garlic bread for a filling dinner idea that takes just 15 minutes to make. Thanks to tortelloni, you can go big and stay home!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6492e9e34b18c31a619ff34a-137aabb6.jpeg
